        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 3: 'Dante knows Vergil, standing beside him, dislikes places like this, but truth be told, neither does he.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 10,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The sprawling laboratory hums with activity, its space woven into an intricate web of cables. They snake across the floor, connecting workstations spaced at regular intervals. Each station is cluttered with glowing monitors and cups of coffee.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 11,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The entire lab feels like a living network, workstations acting as nodes linked by those endless cables.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 12,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Researchers in lab coats—some young, some weathered—weave through the maze of cables, occasionally huddling in small groups to exchange hushed words, their murmurs as constant and indistinct as the hum of a hive.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Dante catches the occasional glance from the researchers, their eyes flicking toward him before darting away. And sometimes, with his exceptional hearing, he even picks up fragments of their quiet conversations.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 306,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": null
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 402,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2915'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Then, abruptly, the murmurs cease. A silence ripples through the room, distant at first but growing louder until—'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Two Chiefs step into view.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Dante', 3: 'Hey, 【kuroname】, how\\'s it going?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'I\\'ll let Asimov explain. He\\'s the expert here.', 3: '20'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The two humans approach the table where the two half-demons are seated. Their previous battle has depleted much of their stamina, and the table is laden with pizzas and drinks, a treat clearly meant for them.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 21,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Also, you two need to behave yourselves from now on.', 3: '22', 4: 'Also, could you two... behave yourselves from now on?', 5: '22'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 22,
        "ActionId": 22,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'A training facility was destroyed during Dante and Vergil\\'s battle.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 23,
        "ActionId": 23,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'I wrote so many reports. They might even dock my bonus.', 3: '24'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 24,
        "ActionId": 24,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Dante watches you wearily rub your forehead across from him, responding with a guilty shrug.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 25,
        "ActionId": 25,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '10'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 26,
        "ActionId": 26,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Dante', 3: 'Sorry, my bad. Guess we got a little carried away.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Dante', 3: 'So your bonus...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'It wasn\\'t docked. Commander Nikola shot down that idea.', 3: '29'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
