        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Asimov', 3: 'About the data retrieved from the Babel Tower...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'As Asimov begins his explanation, Dante and you stop your idle chat. Vergil also shifts his gaze toward Asimov.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'According to Thomas\\' experimental data, his initial research direction was essentially a dead end.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'There were two crucial turning points afterward. First, the Hetero Tower shard; second, the supplementary data. And tracing back to its origins, it\\'s possible that this data involves... Dominik.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Dominik...', 3: '36'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Just possible.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'In fact, the fundamental theory behind Thomas\\' experiment derives from Dominik\\'s early research. One could even say it\\'s the continuation of an incomplete project Dominik abandoned during the Golden Age.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Why didn\\'t Dominik continue the research?', 3: '39'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'For several reasons. A human only has limited energy, after all. Even a polymath like Dominik would need to prioritize theories based on strategic necessity and temporal constraints.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Perhaps Dominik picked up old research again during down time, or perhaps it was always just for fun. Either way, Thomas eventually got his hands on the later data and the Hetero Tower shard, which led him to stumble upon the space-time portal.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '8'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Regrettably, given the collapse of the Babel Tower, we can\\'t obtain any more data.', 4: '1'}"
    },
